
Ranger Help for: trailmark
==========================

SYNTAX:      trailmark <message>
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             underground,mountain,arctic,barren,outside
SLOT COST:   3
BASE SP:     15 sp 
SKILL TYPE:  creation

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to trailmark a message into the surrounding
terrain. Trailmarks can only be seen by other Rangers, however, they
only last for so long. A Ranger can use them to help find his or her
way back or to warn of impending danger around the next turn to other
Rangers.

